# Keep the root build context lean. We install deps and build inside the images,
# so host build artifacts and heavy/irrelevant trees are excluded. Sources that the
# images need (python/agent-runtime/src, examples/live-demo, packages/*, tsconfig.base.json,
# pnpm-*.yaml, all package.json) are intentionally NOT ignored.
**/node_modules
**/dist
.git
.github
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.db
**/.airlock
tools/llama.cpp
models
*.log
.DS_Store
